Comment: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:29.99,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.14,0:01:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Acquired Immunity."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.48,0:01:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are all these images I'm seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're heading this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They just keep flowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}right into my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you, Memory Cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Meteorite shower, people fighting, a messenger from the outside world...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What were those images I just saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why would I have such a gorefest of a dream\N when I'm not even a phagocyte?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It shouldn't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The whole thing felt so abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did I envision the moment the world will end?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case, then was that a vision of the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that dream... Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not just that I've committed\N all past antigen battles to memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...now I have the ability to see the future, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's true, then when that virus shows up,\N the world will come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, Memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough with the mumbo jumbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get on with recording the antigen data, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether or not I can put up a fight\N all depends on your knowledge, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A viral infection has just been detected in the parotid gland.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All immune cells in the area,\N please head to the site immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go! If it's a known antigen,\N we have to mow them down with antibodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, time to get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's that thing hiding in the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that one is. This is so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing? That's one strange virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Memory, is it in your records?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:07.37,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not like the world's definitely going to end just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Use your gift of second sight to find a solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.69,0:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Antigen sighted!{note: he says "antigen" here}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks, Neutrophil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Long time no see, B Cell and Memory Cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.52,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to me, premonition! Come to me! Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened to my third eye? Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.86,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey, is something wrong, Memory Cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. We'll deal with all this,\N so you guys go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-These guys are multiplying like crazy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't believe it! All that fighting that I foresaw is really happening now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure, it seems somewhat different from what I saw with my second sight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but does this mean that my gift is the real deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meaning that the fate of this world is—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there you are, B Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and make some antibodies to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This virus is no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second. I can't make antibodies without any data on the antigens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has to present the antigen first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, forget the antibodies! Just take those guys out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I may be a type of white blood cell,\N but I don't do phagocytosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I specialize in antibody attacks, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Figure something out, useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.85,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the only one who can save the world!\N Focus! Clear your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bizarre virus... A battle... Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.39,0:06:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something's about to come raining down, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea! Come on! My miracle second sight power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:35.12,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What are you doing, Memory? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go present the antigen to\N the commander helper T cell, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.05,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once the antigen's presented, we'll be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.91,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But can we hold out until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Help me look, Memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make do with a similar-looking virus!\N Can't you think of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk to me, B Cell! The future... I'm about to get a glimpse of the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All this talk about the future when we're in a crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind the future! Remember the past, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It happened all too suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From out of the distant sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}way beyond anyone's reach,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a colossal tube appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, a flood of spheres sealed by powers from another world came spilling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's something inside! Inside those capsules!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these things? They're weak as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, totally weak! Could they be any weaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Such pushovers. I wonder what their deal is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should stick to protocol
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and have someone present the antigen\N and preserve the data sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please record the antigen data, alright, Memory Cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that wasn't me seeing the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather images from the past that I was seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.62,0:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vaccination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A preemptive injection of a weakened pathogen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}used to acquire immunity to an antigen\N as a preventative measure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to develop protection against a particular disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The antigenic substance that is administered is called a "vaccine".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come! They're going to try to smother us all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mump!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The system will now launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-check, okay. Initiating deployment protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Target identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Antigens identified. Targets locked-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy charge complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this, you dirty virus! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...the power of acquired immunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Acquired immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Immunity acquired by infection or vaccination after birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, thanks to the power of acquired immunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the pathogens soon vanished without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that only took a second!\N And without antigen presentation, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, B Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good ol' antibodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he was able to make those antibodies without the antigen presentation
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks to my memories, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? Jeez! In the first place, it was you who—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.29,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey! Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There already was an entry on today's virus, listing it as an antigen,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but you were going on and on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,about some prophecy, and you just forgot. That was the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, this guy really dropped the ball today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, um, h-hey, hey, B Cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.29,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mumps virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The virus that causes epidemic parotitis.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Characterized by swelling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of one or both parotid glands, causing difficulty in swallowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is why epidemic parotitis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is also known as the "mumps",\N the plural form of "mump", meaning "grimace".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, look how thorough your records are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we feel ridiculous? After all that toil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it in your head, for goodness sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget this ever happened, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Should I have kept my mouth shut?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems it's over already.{* probably more like "They're saying it's already over."?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm beat.
Comment: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:47.98,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"Peyer's Patch."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the next batch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lactose, sucrose, maltose!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.58,0:12:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is the small intestine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where they process all the nutrients, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what a bustling, pleasant place this is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for showing us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have absolutely no clue about this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it. You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time here too,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but I learned all about the small intestine\N during my erythroblast days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't anyone teach you, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know! Why don't I go get us some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only be a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, neutrophil! You've sure got guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Here we are in the intestines, a single membrane away from 100 trillion teeming bacteria,{* 100 trillion}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and you're totally mellowing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me remind you, this isn't a vacation spot\N for you nonchalant cells to zone out in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a battleground where we immune cells\N lock eyes with the germs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer T...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew you neutrophils were this complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't get your act together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you and your friends will end up massacred, game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? You've got a problem?\N You're the one to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only showing some new red blood cells around
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,to help them do their jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.01,0:13:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean! Enough with the handholding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing the enemy is the only thing that should be on your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hey, both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want to know is, will you be able to respond in an emergency if you're so laid-back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What if, even as we speak,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,there were germs on the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the usual colony of intestinal bacteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being attacked by every last germ in these nutrients!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.77,0:13:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is No. 1146! Bacteria that multiplied\N in the small intestine at D6-18 has landed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The surrounding tissue is being destroyed! Requesting immediate backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer T...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pick this up again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a hand if it comes to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The toxic gas from that bacteria\N is endangering the surrounding cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't stop them, it'll generate carcinogenic metabolites!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to eliminate them right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see you try it, white blood cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you care at all about this intestinal epithelial cell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,your only option is to do whatever we campylobacters say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Campylobacter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One of the types of bacteria that causes infectious enteritis,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}triggering fevers, diarrhea, and stomach pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... A hostage? That's so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we haven't thought this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you murdered so many of our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because your duty is to protect the lives\N of all the normal cells, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, we shouldn't be lounging around here,\N or you might catch us off-guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be standing by inside the intestinal tract.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and catch us if you can, white blood cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't exit this tissue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, Campylobacter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us back that hostage! What are your demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We want you to make these intestines\N a bit more comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,For us campylobacters, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll deliver nutrients to us first\N and eliminate all germs that get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you white blood cells will perform for us every day on the other side of that membrane
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep us entertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy as pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you'll provide us with three meals and a nap per day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and prime real estate in a quiet location\N commanding a fine view
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,where we can build our own colony!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to build a paradise of campylobacters,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,by campylobacters, and for campylobacters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:16:03.23,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}After which, for the sake of maintaining order in perpetuity and for all eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll accept your terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.70,0:16:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we've done that— What? No way! You accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! In that case, we'll release the hostage, but first, do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards slaughtered scores of our friends! Dance some kind of jig!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.72,0:16:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now pulverize each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What the cell is that moron doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I always knew he was a moron,\N but who would've known he was this stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We did as you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then, let the hostage go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you're in such a weakened state,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you probably couldn't catch me if I invaded the tissue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be too pathetic if you died because you turned on each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I just finish you off myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Campylobacter! That's not what we agreed on! Let the hostage—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I care? Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.37,0:17:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You utter fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They were never going to release the hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you not see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You really underestimated the power of a germ!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back here! You're not heading that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, the germ just took off with the hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can't even watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You stupid nonchalant cell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about pesky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have enough strength left to chase after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No. 1146?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Look at us! We're so close to\N that spot that's super-easy to infiltrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no villi there, so it's like\N an easy-access entrance for bacteria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Keep your voice down about that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shush! We can't let them find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in an uproar about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you know what they're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, that would be... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...would you at least spare my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.57,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't do it, Intestinal Epithelial Cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:31.38,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anything but that! Just don't mention that to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, up ahead, there's a spot where both villi and membranes are sparse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I may say so myself, it's about as airtight as a sieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I imagine it would be easily infiltrated by you bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance, would you be talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...this place right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! We're doomed! They found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I have no more use for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yippee! Follow me, you guys! We've invaded the tissues!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on in, we'll have unlimited food\N and a warm place to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll never have to worry about earning our keep again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo! Nutrients!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky us! Look how much there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start gorging ourselves and dividing like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll it be for you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, what'll it be?\N I'm a bacterium! I want all of the food here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, partake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is more or less your Last Supper.\N Please enjoy yourselves to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\N Oh, never mind! I'll just grab whatever—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought you'd never get here, Campylobacter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,An immune cell? Wh-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What good will it do to take us on alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's punishment time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that you couldn't see through all that blatant baiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stooping to dirty tactics like taking a hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate us neutrophils!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a piece of immune tissue within the small intestine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,where we lure in stupid germs like you to massacre!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A Peyer's Patch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Peyer's Patches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mass of immune tissue that can be found within the small intestine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in depressions between villi and areas without any.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They are filled with lymphatic nodules.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These patches play a crucial role in the intestinal immune system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm an M cell, the proprietor of this Peyer's Patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}M cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cells found on the surface of the Peyer's Patch\N which trap bacterial and viral antigens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The captured bacteria and viruses\N are handed off to the dendritic cells
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and presented as antigens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You never caught on, but when you knocked us back, we signaled to our comrades
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that we were going to lure you to the Peyer's Patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...an "M" for "M cell"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Like fair has anything to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that sure worked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, getting him to fall for your trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I kept calling you a moron,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but you really do have a good head\N on your shoulders. I had the wrong idea about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Killer T...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on, try not to mellow out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(400,400)}Try not to mellow out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(500,500)}Try not to mellow out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I seem to have forgotten something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That white blood cell's taking forever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just how long are we going to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.45,0:22:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot to get the red blood cells their tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it back, he's a moron.
Comment: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:09.93,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Comment: 0,0:23:24.93,0:23:24.93,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.87,0:23:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My receptor's picked something up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,White Blood Cell! There's a weird mask on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,De-Dengue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:31.60,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,De-Dengue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode of {\i1}Cells at Work!!{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Dengue Fever/Acne".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Work hard every day!
